sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant NextAuth
    participant Google
    participant JWT Token
    participant Database
    participant API Routes

    Note over User,API Routes: 1. SIGN IN FLOW

    User->>Browser: Click "Sign In"
    Browser->>NextAuth: signIn("google")
    NextAuth->>Google: OAuth redirect
    Google->>User: Show consent screen
    User->>Google: Approve access
    Google->>NextAuth: Return user profile + providerAccountId

    Note over NextAuth,Database: 2. SIGN IN CALLBACK

    NextAuth->>Database: upsertUser({<br/>  provider: "google",<br/>  providerUserId: providerAccountId,<br/>  email, name, imageUrl<br/>})
    Database->>Database: INSERT or UPDATE app_user<br/>ON CONFLICT (provider, providerUserId)
    Database-->>NextAuth: Returns internal user UUID

    Note over NextAuth,JWT Token: 3. JWT CALLBACK

    NextAuth->>JWT Token: jwt callback triggered
    JWT Token->>JWT Token: Store providerAccountId in token<br/>token.providerAccountId = providerAccountId
    JWT Token-->>NextAuth: Token with providerAccountId

    Note over NextAuth,Database: 4. SESSION CALLBACK

    NextAuth->>Database: getUserIdByProviderUserId(<br/>  "google",<br/>  token.providerAccountId<br/>)
    Database->>Database: SELECT id FROM app_user<br/>WHERE provider = "google"<br/>AND provider_user_id = providerAccountId
    Database-->>NextAuth: Returns internal UUID
    NextAuth->>NextAuth: Attach to session:<br/>session.user.id = UUID
    NextAuth-->>Browser: Session with internal UUID

    Note over Browser,API Routes: 5. AUTHENTICATED REQUESTS

    Browser->>API Routes: POST /api/translate<br/>(session cookie sent automatically)
    API Routes->>NextAuth: await auth()
    NextAuth->>JWT Token: Verify & decode token
    JWT Token-->>NextAuth: token.providerAccountId
    NextAuth->>Database: Lookup internal UUID
    Database-->>NextAuth: Returns UUID
    NextAuth-->>API Routes: session.user.id = UUID

    API Routes->>Database: insertTranslation({<br/>  userId: session.user.id,<br/>  inputText, responseJson, ...<br/>})
    Database->>Database: INSERT INTO translation_history<br/>WHERE user_id = UUID
    Database-->>API Routes: Success
    API Routes-->>Browser: Translation response

    Note over Browser,Database: 6. FETCH HISTORY

    Browser->>API Routes: GET /api/history/list
    API Routes->>NextAuth: await auth()
    NextAuth-->>API Routes: session.user.id = UUID
    API Routes->>Database: listLast50(session.user.id)
    Database->>Database: SELECT * FROM translation_history<br/>WHERE user_id = UUID<br/>ORDER BY created_at DESC<br/>LIMIT 50
    Database-->>API Routes: Translation history
    API Routes-->>Browser: History JSON

    Note over Browser,Database: 7. SYNC LOCALSTORAGE

    Browser->>API Routes: POST /api/history/sync<br/>{translations: [...]}
    API Routes->>NextAuth: await auth()
    NextAuth-->>API Routes: session.user.id = UUID

    loop For each translation
        API Routes->>Database: translationExists(UUID, inputText, ...)
        alt Translation doesn't exist
            API Routes->>Database: insertTranslation({<br/>  userId: UUID, ...<br/>})
        else Already exists
            API Routes->>API Routes: Skip (count as success)
        end
    end

    API Routes-->>Browser: {success: N, failed: M}